    "description": "This Thai tom yum-inspired fried rice is full of fragrant flavours. You'll whip up an easy tom yum paste with sriracha, ginger and lime before tossing through rice, veg and juicy king prawns. Plate up with a squeeze of lime for extra zing. Under 600 calories.",
